<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>You're in! | Social Magic with Jen</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:wght@500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&family=Caveat:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #faf7f2;
    --plum: #4e3a5a;
    --coral: #f26b6b;
    --teal: #5fa8a8;
    --gold: #d9a441;
    --ink: #3a3a3a;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .wrap {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Header band */
  .header {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--plum);
    padding: 26px 24px 60px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .logo-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .logo span { color: var(--coral); }

  .tagline {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Signature sparkle accent */
  .sparkle-hero {
    margin-top: 14px;
    display: inline-block;
    animation: pop-in 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) 0.15s both;
  }

  .sparkle-hero svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; }

  @keyframes pop-in {
    0%   { transform: scale(0.4) rotate(-15deg); opacity: 0; }
    100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .sparkle-hero { animation: none; }
  }

  /* Photo moment: warm, personal, overlapping header + card */
  .photo-frame-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    margin-top: -70px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    animation: pop-in 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) 0.05s both;
  }

  .photo-frame {
    width: 148px;
    height: 148px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 6px solid #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(78, 58, 90, 0.22);
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Card content */
  .card {
    max-width: 560px;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin: 20px 20px 40px 20px;
    padding: 8px 36px 40px 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(78, 58, 90, 0.12);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 30px;
    color: var(--plum);
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .subhead {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--coral);
    margin: 0 0 22px 0;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 18px 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px dashed #e6dcd0;
    margin: 28px 0;
  }

  /* Confirmation callout */
  .confirm-box {
    background-color: var(--cream);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--teal);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .confirm-box .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
    font-size: 19px;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
  }

  .confirm-box h2 {
    font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--plum);
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }

  .confirm-box p {
    font-size: 15px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* What's coming */
  .whats-coming {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .whats-coming h3 {
    font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--plum);
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }

  /* Social buttons */
  .social-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 24px 0 4px 0;
  }

  .social-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 11px 22px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .social-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .social-btn.ig { background-color: var(--coral); }
  .social-btn.li { background-color: var(--teal); }
  .social-btn.fb { background-color: var(--gold); }

  /* Missing email section */
  .missing-email {
    max-width: 560px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 36px 56px 36px;
  }

  .missing-email p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #7a7280;
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
  }

  .mail-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    background-color: var(--plum);
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 30px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .mail-btn:hover {
    background-color: #3d2e48;
  }

  a:focus-visible, .social-btn:focus-visible, .mail-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--gold);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .card { padding: 8px 24px 32px 24px; margin: 16px 16px 32px 16px; }
    h1 { font-size: 25px; }
    .missing-email { padding: 0 20px 48px 20px; }
    .photo-frame { width: 120px; height: 120px; }
    .photo-frame-wrap { margin-top: -58px; }
    .header { padding: 24px 20px 50px 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrap">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo-row">
      <p class="logo">Social<span>Magic</span></p>
      <p class="tagline">with jen</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sparkle-hero">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M22 2 L26 18 L42 22 L26 26 L22 42 L18 26 L2 22 L18 18 Z" fill="#d9a441"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="photo-frame-wrap">
    <img src="/images/hello-gorgeous-mug.jpg" alt="Jen holding a mug that says hello gorgeous" class="photo-frame">
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h1>You're in!</h1>
    <p class="subhead">so glad you're here &#10022;</p>

    <p>Seriously, welcome. You just took the first step toward telling your story with more clarity and a lot less overwhelm, and I couldn't be happier you're here.</p>

    <div class="confirm-box">
      <p class="eyebrow">one small thing first</p>
      <h2>Check your inbox</h2>
      <p>I hate spam as much as you do, so I want to make sure you actually want to be here. You'll get a confirmation email any minute now. Just click the link inside, and you're officially on the list.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="whats-coming">
      <h3>What happens next</h3>
      <p>Once you confirm, you'll start getting The Spark: weekly tips on telling your story with clarity, building marketing systems that sound like you, and using AI as a tool that amplifies your voice, never replaces it.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider">

    <p style="text-align:center; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-size: 19px; color: var(--gold);">while you wait, let's connect &#10022;</p>

    <div class="social-row">
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/socialmagicwithjen/" class="social-btn ig">Instagram</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jenniferlsanders" class="social-btn li">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/socialmagicwithjen/" class="social-btn fb">Facebook</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="missing-email">
    <p>Didn't see the confirmation email? Check your spam folder first, then reach out directly, I'll make sure you're on the list.</p>
    <a href="mailto:jen@socialmagicwithjen.com?subject=I%20didn%27t%20get%20my%20confirmation%20email" class="mail-btn">Email Jen Directly &rarr;</a>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
